data.description: Great investment opportunity in Sylvan Beach! Two family home with 2 car garage and a vacant building lot! Yes, TLC is needed but just look at this great location, just a couple blocks from the Beach, Oneida Lake, Fish Creek and resort action with great parking and yard! Located just outside of the hustle bustle of the “beach” but you can still take the sidewalk in town to everything!  The first floor boasts 3-4 bedrooms, large living room with fireplace and large each in kitchen, bonus space and a full bath with laundry. The 2nd story has one bedroom, kitchen, living room and full bath. Each apartment has its own electric and hot water heater but share an oil fired boiler. Adequate insulation and new windows have been upgraded throughout. This sale also includes tax ID # 236.020-1-31. Also listed as multi family home MLS#S1496293.
